snippet.title: Make a Good Mega Man Level Contest 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The contest results will be streamed on May 20th (likely around 10 AM EST) on Flashman85's twitch channel. The streams will be archived and re-uploaded to YouTube at a later time as well. Important links can be found below.

Link to Flashman85's twitch channel:
https://www.twitch.tv/flashman85

Flashman85's YouTube channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtAyZh5WF1uceV6LVIHWASQ

MaGMML2 Thread on Sprites INC:
http://sprites-inc.co.uk/showthread.php?tid=1688

Metalltool's Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/user/Metalltool

And a link to his awesome MM10 Wily 3 remix that was used in this video:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ul603rxE1aY
